----

This work reproduces the FastGRNN algorithm originally proposed in:

  Kusupati, A., Singh, M., Bhatia, K., Kumar, A., Jain, P., Varma, M.
  "FastGRNN: A Fast, Accurate, Stable and Tiny Kilobyte Sized Gated
   Recurrent Neural Network." NeurIPS 2018.

----

This work uses the HAPT (Human Activities and Postural Transitions)
dataset, which is the property of the original authors:

  Reyes-Ortiz, J.-L., Oneto, L., Samà, A., Parra, X., Anguita, D.
  "Transition-Aware Human Activity Recognition Using Smartphones."
  Neurocomputing, 171:754--767, 2016.

The dataset is publicly available from the UCI Machine Learning
Repository under the terms specified there.
